## RedBlackTree.entries() method

Returns a new iterator object that contains an \*\*array of `[key, value]`<!-- -->\*\* for each element in the red black tree in in-order.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
entries(): IterableIterator<[K, V]>;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

IterableIterator&lt;\[K, V\]&gt;
